        <li class="comment byuser comment-author-gamenobel even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1"  id="li-comment-185711" itemtype="http://schema.org/Comment" itemscope="" itemprop="comment">
            <div id="comment-185711" class="comment-block">
                    <div class="comment-avatar pm-relative">
                        <a href="http://www.woshipm.com/u/165565" target="_blank"><img src="http://wen.woshipm.com/assets/images/def_head.jpg?imageView2/1/w/40/h/40/q/100" alt="" height="40" width="40" class="avatar"></a>
                                            </div>
                <div class="comment-info">
                    <div class="comment-meta">
                                                                            <div class="comment-author" itemprop="author"><a href="http://www.woshipm.com/u/165565" target="_blank">gamenobel</a><span class="des"></span></div>
                                  
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment-content" itemprop="description">
                    <p>如果一个用户组下面又分组长和组员，<br />
q1：组长和组员的权限是不同的要怎么分<br />
q2：组长可以创建组员（用户管理），但给组员分配权限既不能高于他自己，又和他自己有区别，这个时候就矛盾了，怎么细分</p>
                </div>

                    <div class="u-clearfix comment-bottom"><span class="comment-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2016-11-16T20:59:18+08:00">2016/11/16</span><span class="comment-reply-link u-floatRight u-cursorPointer" onclick="return addComment.moveForm('comment-185711', '185711', 'respond', '440765')"><span class="fa fa-comment"></span>回复</span></div>
            </div>
