            <div id="comment-187367" class="comment-block">
                    <div class="comment-avatar pm-relative">
                        <a href="http://www.woshipm.com/u/162710" target="_blank"><img src="http://wen.woshipm.com/assets/images/def_head.jpg?imageView2/1/w/40/h/40/q/100" alt="" height="40" width="40" class="avatar"></a>
                                            </div>
                <div class="comment-info">
                    <div class="comment-meta">
                                                                            <div class="comment-author" itemprop="author"><a href="http://www.woshipm.com/u/162710" target="_blank">desperado</a><span class="color-noraml">回复</span><a href="#comment-185711">gamenobel</a></div>
                                  
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment-content" itemprop="description">
                    <p>这里创建用户组的目的只是为了方便群体授权（该部门所有人都有的权限），权限并不能包含用户管理。而你说的分等级应该在角色划分时确定</p>
                </div>

